The Board of Estimates, at appropriate intervals, shall engage an independent firm of certified
public accountants to audit:

   (1)the financial transactions of the Department of Audits; and

   (2)the comprehensive annual financial report of the City.
The Board of Estimates, at appropriate intervals, shall engage an independent firm of certified
public accountants to audit:

The independent firm of certified public accountants shall make reports of its audits,
examinations, and recommendations to the Board of Estimates.







